  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparing the Efficacy of Ultrasound Guided Hyaluronic Injection with Ultrasound Guided
      Corticosteroid Injection in Treatment of Trigger Finger
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Randomized controlled trial which designed to compare the success rate, recurrence rate and
      functional outcomes of patients with trigger finger whom was treated with ultrasound guided
      hyaluronic acid injection to ultrasound guided corticosteroid injection
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
